Again, I don't like adding the idea of being able to charm undead unless it would mean being able to have 2 pets.<BR>I would rather see a spec absorb damage buff that stacks with the baseline and would put us on level with the chain equivalent wearing mezzers.<BR>I would also like to see nearsight added. I don't think it would matter if 2 Albion Casters had this spell. They are both underplayed classes and we already suffer from abilities being watered down through more classes.
